Solace;;2015;;R;;Crime,Drama,Mystery;;6.4;;Afonso Poyart;;Anthony Hopkins,Jeffrey Dean Morgan,Abbie Cornish,Colin Farrell,Matt Gerald,Jose Pablo Cantillo,Marley Shelton,Xander Berkeley,Kenny Johnson,Joshua Close,Sharon Lawrence,Janine Turner,Luisa Moraes,Jordan Woods-Robinson,Niyi Oni,Carter Godwin,Autumn Dial,Tara Arroyave;;A psychic doctor, John Clancy (Sir Anthony Hopkins), works with an F.B.I. Special Agent (Jeffrey Dean Morgan) in search of serial killer Charles Ambrose (Colin Farrell). After having lived in isolation for two years since the death of his daughter, Clancy is asked by his friend Joe, an F.B.I. Special Agent, to help him solve several murders committed by a serial killer. The problem is that Ambrose is also psychic and far ahead of Clancy.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1291570/